description:
Hyper Dive is a 1000 NFT collection of animated cubes. 

From the 26.04 at 18:00 CET (6pm) is it so far, then starts our new Sale of the HyperDive NFT's a project that has arisen in the course of our achievement "1000 followers on twitter". 

We will give away 1000 NFT's at one IOTA each. 

Why?
Simply to celebrate our community on the one hand and on the other hand to make other people aware of the advantages of IOTA (no fees). 

A total of 38 different variants of NFT's are waiting for you, which differ in their colors or significantly in the texture of the animated cubes. 

Some of them are rarer some again appear more often. 

What happens to the earnings?
Since this is a community action, all revenue generated by Dust Protection will be given to IOTA based projects.

You have the opportunity to submit a project proposal on our Twitter account in the posts that have been published on this topic so far.  5 of these proposed projects that are received by the end of the week (29.04.) will then be determined in a large poll by the community and receive equal shares of the accumulated revenue through this sale.
name: Hyper Dive
